FBIS3-52280 "drnes002_a_94003" FBIS-NES-94-002 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Jan 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria FIS Said To Begin Television Transmission JN0301152894 London AL-HAYAH in Arabic 1 Jan 94 pp 1, 4 JN0301152894 London AL-HAYAH Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [By Jamal Khashuqji in Jeddah] [Excerpt] Sources of the dissolved Islamic Salvation Front and citizens in Algiers who were contacted by AL-HAYAH over the telephone confirmed that the front began television transmission last Monday [27 December] under the name of Salvation Television, which was monitored in the capital. By this, the front is adding clandestine television transmission to its radio transmission named al-Wafa' Radio, which regularly transmits every Saturday from an unknown place. [passage omitted]
